Hashtag #voyagedgem for a chance to win a memelist from @memeland!

How to join:
1. Take a photo of a hidden gem in your local area and post it on Instagram with the hashtag #voyagedgem . You must include the location in the post.
2. Follow our page @voyaged and become a member in the MEMELAND discord server (link in bio)
3. Only one submission per account allowed. We will not consider entries by accounts with more than 1 submission.
4. You cannot submit your old photos for this contest, meaning your submission (photo) must be published on Instagram on or after 29th July 2022.
5. Contest ends at 16:00 UTC on 3rd August 2022. Winners will be announced in this post on 9th August and receive a DM from @voyaged.

Terms & Conditions:
This contest is not sponsored, endorsed, or administered by Instagram.
9GAG reserves the right to make the final decision in case of any dispute.

Photo credit: Joel Fulgencio on Unsplash

Join our 'Voyaged With Animals' campaign for a chance to get featured on @voyaged! 
Just hashtag #voyagedwithanimals in the photos you posted on your feed of animals you spotted during your trip or travelled with.

Photos can be old ones you have uploaded a while ago and there is no limit to the number of submissions you make. Just remember to include the exact location name in the post.

3-5 winners will be featured on @voyaged.

Campaign period: 21-23 Jul 2022
